Package: rmlirdsl
Type: Package
Title: R DSL for MLIR R Dialect
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("R", "DSL", email = "r-dsl@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Build a small AST in R and lower it to an MLIR dialect with
    support for vectors and matrices as tensors.
